translation: Salutation to Him, Who holds the disc in His hand, He hath manifested Himself without elements.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ ੳੁਗ੍ਰ ਦਾੜੰ ॥ ਮਹਾ ਗ੍ਰਿਸਟ ਗਾੜੰ ॥੮੯॥
transliteration: Namo Ougra Daaran|| Mahaa Grist Gaddan||89||
translation: Salutation to Him, who hath sharp grinder teeth, which are thick and strong.89.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ ਭੀਰ ਤੋਪੰ ॥ ਜਿਨੈ ਸਤ੍ਰੁ ਘੋਪੰ ॥
transliteration: Namo Toor Topan|| Jinai Satru Ghopan||
translation: Salutation to Him, who hath the arrows and the cannon, who hath destroyed the enemies.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ ਧੋਪ ਪੱਟੰ ॥ ਜਿਨੈ ਦੁਸਟ ਦੱਟੰ ॥੯੦॥
transliteration: Namo Dhop Pattan|| Jinai Doust Dattan||90||
translation: Salutation to Him, Who holds the straight sword and the bayonet, Who hath reporimanded the tyrants.90.
I salute all the weapons of various names.
I salute all kinds of armour.91.

gurmukhi: ਮੇਰੁ ਕਰੋ ਤ੍ਰਿਣ ਤੇ ਮੁਹਿ ਜਾਹਿ ਗਰੀਬ ਨਿਵਾਜ ਨ ਦੂਸਰ ਤੋ ਸੋ ॥
transliteration: Mer(u) Daro Trin Te Muh(i) Jaah(i) Daroob Niwaaj Na Doosar To So||
translation: There is no other support for the poor except Thee, who hath made me a mountain from a straw.

gurmukhi: ਭੂਲ ਛਿਮੋ ਹਮਰੀ ਪ੍ਰਭ ਅਾਪਨ ਭੂਲਨਹਾਰ ਕਹੂੰ ਕੋੳੂ ਮੋ ਸੋ ॥
transliteration: Bhool Chimo Hamroo Prabh Aapan Bhoolanhaar Kahoon Ko( i)  Mo So||
translation: O Lord! Forgive me for my mistakes, because who is there so much blunderhead like me?

gurmukhi: ਸੇਵ ਕਰੀ ਤੁਮਰੀ ਤਿਨ ਕੇ ਸਭ ਹੀ ਗ੍ਹਿ ਦੇਖੀਅਤ ਦ੍ਰਬ ਭਰੋ ਸੋ ॥
transliteration: Sev Daroo Toumroo Tin Ke Sabh Hoo Grih Dekhooat Drab Bdaro So||
translation: Those who have served Thee, there seems wealth and self-confidence in all there homes.

gurmukhi: ਯਾ ਕਲ ਮੈਂ ਸਭ ਕਾਲ ਕ੍ਰਿਪਾਨ ਕੇ ਭਾਹੀ ਭੁਜਾਨ ਕੋ ਭਾਰੀ ਭਰੋਸੋ ॥੯੨॥
transliteration: Yaa Kal Main Sabh Kaal Kridaan Ke Bhar(i) Bhujaan Ko Bhar(i) Bdaroso||92||
translation: In this Iron age, the supreme trust is only for KAL, Who is the Sword-incarnate and hath mighty arms.92.

gurmukhi: ਸੁੰਭ ਨਿਸੁੰਭ ਸੇ ਕੋਟ ਨਿਸਾਚਰ ਜਾਹਿ ਛਿਨੇਕ ਬਿਖੈ ਹਨ ਡਾਰੇ ॥
transliteration: Sounbh Nisounbh Se Kot Nisaachar Jaah(i) Chhinek Bikhai Han Ddare||
translation: He, who hath destroyed millions of demons like Sumbh and Nisumbh in and instant.

gurmukhi: ਧੂਮਰਲੋਚਨ ਚੰਡ ਅੌ ਮੁੰਡ ਸੇ ਮਾਹਖ ਸੇ ਪਲ ਬੀਚ ਨਿਵਾਰੇ ॥
transliteration: Dhoomarlochanndchannd Au Mounnd Se Maahakh Se Pal Boodhe Nivdare||
translation: Who hath annihilated in and instant the demons like Dhumarlochan, Chand, Mund and Mahishasura.
